      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Inana , lady of the E-ana , his lady , Ea-niša , ( Šulgi's ) consort , dedicated this ( bead ) for the well-being of Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad ."
